oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Hatch Show Print Price List
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Hatch Show Print (Firm); Offset printing;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: One color print (black on white) featuring a price list for Hatch Show Print posters and a checklist to use when ordering posters. This same information also appears on the reverse side of the "Howdy Neighbor" letter. This text was probably printed from a black and white negative, which would have also been used to create a corresponding printing plate.
